Package: silentSubstitutor
Title: Creates Silent Substitution Stimuli for Vision Science
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Cord", "Huchzermeyer", , "c.huchzermeyer@posteo.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0408-8981"))
Description: The app enables the calculation of photoreceptor-directed, periodic stimuli based on dual, triple, or quadruple silent substitution for use in electroretinography.
